    <p>{`If you need a `}<strong parentName="p">{`Database User`}</strong>{` which should only have read permissions, select `}<strong parentName="p">{`Read-Only`}</strong>{` in the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Permissions`}</strong>{` drop down.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
