    <h2 {...{
      "id": "database-backups"
    }}>{`Database Backups`}</h2>
    <p>{`All databases will be automatically backup once per night at 4:15 AM.`}</p>
    <p>{`If you have smaller databases, you can change the cron job to run more frequently like twice a day. `}</p>
    <p>{`To change the schedule of the database backup task, do the following:`}</p>
    <p>{`1) Login via `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "users#ssh-login"
      }}>{`SSH`}</a>{` to your server and become `}<strong parentName="p">{`root`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`sudo su root
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`2) Switch the user to `}<strong parentName="p">{`clp-admin`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`sudo su clp-admin
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`3) Edit the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Cron Jobs`}</strong>{` of the user.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
