              }}></path></svg></span>{`Database Backup Program`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-content"
      }}><p parentName="div">{`For the backup, `}<strong parentName="p">{`CloudPanel`}</strong>{` uses the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Database Backup Program`}</strong>{` `}<a parentName="p" {...{
